Package: cdmAmsIf
Title: Implementation of CDM Small-Scale Methodology AMS-I.F
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides tidyverse-aligned tooling to implement the Clean Development Mechanism
    small-scale methodology AMS-I.F "Renewable electricity generation for captive use and
    mini-grids".
    Functions translate numbered equations, applicability conditions, and calculation
    workflows into reproducible R code and include simulation utilities for demonstration
    and testing purposes.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
